text: Oscar Fuentes (born 10 July 1954) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
